  "response": "There are several reputable solar panel installation providers in Novato, California. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **SolarCraft** - They are a local company with a strong reputation for quality installations and customer service.\n2. **Sunrun** - This national company offers various solar solutions and has a good track record in the area.\n3. **SunPower by Solar Technologies** - Known for high-efficiency solar panels and excellent service.\n4. **North Bay Solar Electric** - A smaller, local provider that offers personalized service and quality installations.\n\nWhen choosing a solar panel installation provider, consider factors such as customer reviews, warranties, financing options, and the types of solar panels they offer. It's also a good idea to get multiple quotes to compare prices and services.",
